supportDesc.extent: 159 leaves : 250 x 130 (175 x 67) mm, bound to 250 x 130 mm
supportDesc.foliation: Modern foliation added in pencil, upper left recto; catchwords every verso, lower left, some taped over.

layoutDesc.layout: 21 long lines with marginalia; diagrams on almost every page, set in text and in the margins.

binding.p: Brown leather with blind stamped central mandorla, two pendants along the vertical axis and frame.

history.provenance: Presumed to be a gift of David Eugene Smith, 1931-1934.
